# BoomPass IETF Draft Pipeline

This repository automates the conversion of an IETF-compliant Markdown draft into XML using `markdown2rfc`, with optional GitHub Actions integration.

---

## 1. `package.json`

```json
{
  "name": "boompass-ietf-drafts",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "description": "Internet-Draft conversion pipeline for BoomPass",
  "scripts": {
    "convert": "markdown2rfc specs/draft-okeamah-boomchainlabs-boompass-protocol.md specs/xml/draft-okeamah-boomchainlabs-boompass-protocol.xml"
  },
  "devDependencies": {
    "@martinthomson/markdown2rfc": "^2.2.4"
  }
}
